channel.title: DJMAX Technika 3
channel.description:
So, DJMAX Technika 3 is coming out this month. I'm sure most of you don't play it, but it's a freakin' awesome Korean rhythm game. You play by touching the notes on the screen, and rack up points so you can get into the Platinum Member's Club. It's also going to be released for the PSVista as well; The music is as great as always.
Video: [url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ryqd91G0Zi0&list=FLLlXWH1VyiC18WaPd1CHkHg&index=10']https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ryqd91G0Zi0[/url]
